              "description": {
                "paragraph": [
                  "Enjoy stable Wi-Fi connections, even in the kitchen and bedroom, with this TP-LINK Archer AX4400 Wi-Fi 6 router. High-power FEM, six antennas, beamforming, and 4T4R structures combine to adapt Wi-Fi coverage to perfectly fit your home and concentrate signal strength towards your devices. Easily handle dozens of devices streaming and gaming at the same time: OFDMA and MU-MIMO combine to future-proof your home network by providing greater capacity to connect more devices."
                ],
                "descriptionLineSize": 2,
                "bullets": [
                  "Dual-band router reaches speeds up to 4400Mbps (3843Mbps on the 5GHz band and 574Mbps on the 2.4GHz band)",
                  "Features dual-band Wi-Fi 6 connectivity, 1 x Gigabit WAN port, and 4 x Gigabit LAN ports",
                  "1.5GHz triple-core CPU handles data throughput up to multi-gigs and minimizes the latency within your home network, delivering you a smooth experience",
                  "Dimensions: 2\"H x 10.3\"W x 5.7\"D",
                  "TP-LINK Tether app allows you to set up the router in minutes",
                  "Meets or exceeds the FCC, CE, RoHS standards",
                  "Comes equipped with the wireless technology Wi-Fi 6 for faster speeds, greater capacity, and reduced network congestion",
                  "Router supports all previous 802.11 standards and all Wi-Fi devices",
                  "Achieve a highly strong and reliable Wi-Fi coverage with this router as it focuses signal strength to your devices using the beamforming technology and six antennas",
                  "Supports MU-MIMO and OFDMA to reduce congestion and quadruple the average throughput",
                  "Equipped with the top structure of 4T4R and HE160 on the 5GHz band to enable 3.8Gbps ultrafast connection",
                  "Premium security services keep your home network safe with cutting-edge features for network and IoT protection",
                  "USB 3.0 port enables easy media sharing and private cloud building",
                  "Box includes: Wi-Fi router, power adapter, RJ45 Ethernet cable, and quick installation guide",
                  "Firewall security: SPI firewall, IP and MAC address binding",
                  "Supported VPN servers: OpenVPN, PPTP VPN",
                  "Parental controls restrict Internet access time and content for children's devices",
                  "Comes in black"
                ]
              },
